I can't say from my experience that I understand the mediocre reviews for Khotan.
My wife and I thoroughly enjoyed our meal.
We didn't have the sushi and stuck to mainstream pekinese type dishes; lettuce wraps, edamame (ok, they're Japaneze), lobster curry and sweet&sour chicken, all of which were fresh and tasty.
